{"text_id":218399,"tokens":["The"," debate"," over"," whether"," the"," United"," States"," should"," switch"," to"," a"," popular"," vote"," system"," for"," electing"," the"," President"," has"," been"," ongoing"," for"," many"," years","."," Some"," argue"," that"," the"," current"," Electoral"," College"," system"," is"," safe","guarded"," to"," protect"," the"," interests"," of"," smaller"," states",","," while"," others"," believe"," that"," a"," popular"," vote"," would"," lead"," to"," a"," more"," representative"," and"," democratic"," election"," process",".","\n","One"," of"," the"," main"," benefits"," of"," a"," popular"," vote"," system"," is"," that"," it"," would"," eliminate"," the"," possibility"," of"," electoral"," vote"," splits",","," which"," occurs"," when"," the"," winning"," candidate"," does"," not"," receive"," the"," majority"," of"," the"," popular"," vote","."," This"," happened"," most"," recently"," in"," the"," ","2","0","0","0"," presidential"," election",","," when"," George"," W","."," Bush"," won"," the"," election"," despite"," losing"," the"," popular"," vote"," to"," Al"," Gore"," by"," over"," ","5","0","0",",","0","0","0"," votes","."," A"," popular"," vote"," system"," would"," ensure"," that"," the"," candidate"," who"," receives"," the"," most"," support"," from"," the"," public"," would"," also"," win"," the"," election",","," providing"," more"," clarity"," and"," potentially"," reducing"," political"," divisi","veness",".","\n","Another"," benefit"," of"," a"," popular"," vote"," system"," is"," that"," it"," could"," increase"," voter"," turnout","."," With"," the"," current"," system",","," voters"," in"," states"," that"," are"," considered"," safe"," for"," one"," party"," or"," another"," may"," feel"," that"," their"," votes"," are"," not"," necessarily"," impacting"," the"," outcome"," of"," the"," election"," and"," thus"," choose"," not"," to"," vote","."," However",","," a"," popular"," vote"," system"," would"," ensure"," that"," every"," vote"," counts",","," potentially"," inspiring"," more"," people"," to"," participate"," in"," the"," election"," process",".","\n","Yet",","," there"," are"," also"," drawbacks"," to"," a"," popular"," vote","."," Smaller"," states",","," particularly"," those"," that"," are"," more"," rural",","," fear"," that"," their"," political"," power"," would"," be"," diminished"," under"," a"," popular"," vote"," system",","," as"," their"," votes"," would"," be"," diluted"," by"," more"," populous"," states","."," This"," is"," a"," legitimate"," concern"," as"," it"," could"," lead"," to"," a"," situation"," where"," candidates"," focus"," their"," efforts"," on"," large"," metropolitan"," areas",","," potentially"," neglecting"," the"," needs"," and"," concerns"," of"," less"," populous"," regions",".","\n","In"," conclusion",","," while"," both"," systems"," have"," their"," merits"," and"," drawbacks",","," the"," popular"," vote"," system"," boasts"," several"," advantages","."," It"," promotes"," fairness"," by"," ensuring"," that"," the"," candidate"," who"," receives"," the"," most"," support"," nationwide"," is"," elected",","," and"," could"," increase"," voter"," turnout"," by"," making"," every"," vote"," count","."," However",","," there"," are"," valid"," concerns"," about"," the"," potential"," dilution"," of"," political"," power"," for"," smaller"," states","."," Ultimately",","," the"," decision"," of"," whether"," or"," not"," to"," switch"," to"," a"," popular"," vote"," system"," involves"," balancing"," these"," various"," considerations"," and"," seeking"," a"," system"," that"," best"," represents"," the"," interests"," of"," all"," Americans","."," ","\n","Would"," you"," like"," me"," to"," generate"," a"," new"," essay"," on"," this"," topic"," from"," a"," different"," perspective","?"],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"cohere","label":1}